name: Enpass Data File
summary: Learn about .WALLETX files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: After creating a backup you can restore the information at a later time. Choose the Restore... option and browse to the file location to restore the file.
NOTE: Enpass Technologies replaced WALLETX files with .ENPASSBACKUP files when it released version 6 of Enpass.

description: Data file created by Enpass, an application used to manage passwords and other confidential information; stores an encrypted backup of your information that can only be opened by Enpass software.
